narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: Different thoughts in organic chemistry. I learned how to solve a problem and how to design experiments.
Many of the seminars were very interesting

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: More communication about the course expectations.
The speakers this semester were all excellent. I attended every organic seminar.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: Yes, I would. You can talk with some of the greatest scientists during the lecture and learn their thoughts.
